race.description: Follow Thedogssa On X (N/P) Tg 5+W Series 3 F
race.comment: BOURNE MODEL (2) was quickly out of the tricky draw with a fast early sectional and clocked 30.49 with a 0.8 lengths win at Angle Park over 530m. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. In great recent form and expected to measure up again. SLICK ANGEL (1) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fourth (31.04) at Angle Park latest. Has a good record at this journey. Leading chance. DAINTREE SHADY (8) is better than last start when fourth (30.93) in a Special conditions race at Angle Park over 530m. Has a good record at this journey. Must be included in calculations. WOODSIDE JOHNNY (3) was in the money last start and wasn't beaten far - should feature again.
